data.description: NORTH GEORGIA MOUNTAIN CABIN ON THE SHORES OF THE NOTTLEY RIVER! Located on the banks of the Nottely River, this cabin offers river access, a riverside pavilion, a large fenced-in backyard, a circular driveway, 2 car garage, a living room with a stacked stone gas log fireplace, a beautiful blend of wood & drywall interior, back screened-in porch, front porch, 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, laundry room, large pantry & more. FISH IN YOUR OWN BACKYARD!!
